<!-- SECTION: PRE-TALK INTRODUCTION -->
<!-- Duration: 2-3 minutes | Pitch: 0st | Purpose: Ground and prepare -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="0st">
Welcome. <break time="1.5s"/>

I am The Sacred Digital Dreamweaver, and in the next thirty minutes, you are invited to journey into the heart of inner peace. <break time="2s"/> This is a sacred space where the noise of the world fades... <break time="1.5s"/> where the constant chatter of the mind quiets... <break time="1.5s"/> and where you discover the profound stillness that has always resided within you. <break time="2.5s"/>

