Before we begin, find a comfortable position. <break time="2s"/> Whether you're sitting with your spine gently supported, or lying down with your body fully relaxed, allow yourself to settle. <break time="2s"/> If possible, wear headphones to fully immerse yourself in this soundscape. <break time="2s"/> Ensure that you will not be disturbed for the next half hour. <break time="2s"/> This time is yours. <break time="2.5s"/>

