The fragrance here... <break time="2s"/> oh, the fragrance. <break time="2.5s"/> White jasmine blossoms release their perfume into the evening air. <break time="2s"/> The earthiness of rich, ancient soil grounds you. <break time="2s"/> And underneath it all, the subtle scent of incense... <break time="2s"/> sandalwood and myrrh... <break time="2s"/> sacred and timeless. <break time="4s"/>

