"You have carried so much," The Healer says softly. <break time="2.5s"/> Her voice is like honey... <break time="2s"/> like the sound of wind chimes in a gentle breeze. <break time="3s"/> "It is time to release your burdens." <break time="3.5s"/>

She places her luminous hand over your heart. <break time="2.5s"/> You feel warmth spreading from that point... <break time="2s"/> golden warmth that flows like liquid sunlight through your chest... <break time="2s"/> down your arms... <break time="1.5s"/> through your torso... <break time="1.5s"/> into your legs. <break time="3s"/> Wherever this warmth touches, tension melts away. <break time="2.5s"/> Old hurts dissolve. <break time="2.5s"/> Fears evaporate like morning fog. <break time="4s"/>

