<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="0st">
Welcome back. <break time="2.5s"/>

The peace you experienced in that sacred garden is not a fleeting thing. <break time="2s"/> It has been anchored into your being. <break time="2.5s"/> And I want to give you several ways to reconnect with it whenever you need to. <break time="3.5s"/>

